{"tid":2338082,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"住嚮支那領事館對面 可以點撚9佢地","createTime":"2020-12-23T19:15:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T03:30:45.000Z","uid":123774,"like":32,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"7f0cade477b9f22bb0bf88281fbebd9326f35254","tid":2338082,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T19:15:14.000Z","msg":"外國撚<br />\n住響支那領事館對面<br />\n<br />\n每日24/7睇到佢地出入<br />\n觀察所見佢哋平時唔多外出<br />\n淨係幾隻50-60+老支閪夜晚出嚟散步<br />\n<br />\n觀察左佢哋已經將平時領事館垃圾站<br />\n搬咗去100米以外<br />\n屋頂有幾隻大衛星碟<br />\n<br />\n我入左佢地紅圈<br />\n佢哋認為我係愛國藍屍<br />\n支那商會同埋一堆中資機構<br />\n地址同人物背景已經有掌握<br />\n<br />\n可以點長期撚9佢地<br />\n又唔會俾佢地發現"},{"pid":"cedee3ca19e1d33f698603c8133b124fff199059","tid":2338082,"uid":284432,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T19:21:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bfffa41da1690018ec9d5780d8a4527de8fa0abb","tid":2338082,"uid":284432,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T19:22:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1889487f56fa37320b30464e97ab89b7fbb346ec","tid":2338082,"uid":123774,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"cedee3ca19e1d33f698603c8133b124fff199059","tid":2338082,"uid":284432,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T19:21:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T19:29:23.000Z","msg":"其實我跟蹤左佢哋一段時間<br />\n影左佢地幾間公司門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a30d5bacaf18a92eadfc47f2ad32ce8a1b1c2351","tid":2338082,"uid":123774,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bfffa41da1690018ec9d5780d8a4527de8fa0abb","tid":2338082,"uid":284432,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T19:22:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T19:30:35.000Z","msg":"出入只係下等人 真係唔係制裁個班<br />\n<br />\n有乜日常生活整9佢地仲爽d"},{"pid":"29f3c16d070290a81b13801bc47056b82746645f","tid":2338082,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23